<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_455" id="227r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_455_r2l7">Otten <expan>Heberſrewt<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_455_r2l8"><expan>Vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dienſt beuor / <expan>Lıeb<ex>er</ex></expan> Ott / Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt / <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_455_r2l9">ſache <expan>vveg<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>s</expan> <expan>kuntſchaftman<ex>n</ex>s</expan> <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> bey vns mit <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_455_r2l10"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>derbt</expan> <expan>vvord<ex>e</ex>n</expan> iſt / <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brıef wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> / . vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_455_r2l11">ıſt es / daʒ Jr <expan>ſelb<ex>er</ex></expan> darvmb cʒü vns herein <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet / So </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_455_r2l12"><expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir ew vnd den <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> die mit ew <expan>reit<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnſer geleitte </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_455_r2l13"><expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vngeu<ex>er</ex>lıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vnd wöllen ewr rede vor <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> Rate </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_455_r2l14">hören vnd ew müntlich ein <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> darauf <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_455" id="227r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Otten <expan>Hebersrewt<ex>er</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dienst bevor. <expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        Ott, als ir uns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> sache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> und
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>s</expan>
<expan>kuntschaftman<ex>n</ex>s,</expan>
<expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> bey uns mit <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>derbt</expan>
<expan>word<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ist, <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brief wol
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> und ist es, daz ir
                                <expan>selb<ex>er</ex></expan> darumb czü uns herein
                                <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet, so
                            <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir ew und den
                            <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, die mit ew
                        <expan>reit<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, unser geleitte <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>
<expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und wöllen ewr rede vor
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> rate hören und ew müntlich ein
                                <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> darauf
                            <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n.</expan></ab>
</div>
</div></body>
